name: Wood Rat
desc: Charming, appealing, clever. Quick-witted and sociable. Hoarders and wasters.

name: Wood Ox
desc: Methodical, routine. Dependable, sullen. Dislikes competition.

name: Fire Tiger
desc: Fiercely competitive; rash, brave, magnetic. Proud, unrestrained.

name: Fire Rabbit
desc: Gregarious, but aloof. Avoids confrontation. Benevolent, inclined to gossip. Artistic.

name: Earth Dragon
desc: Exotic. vital. Elegant, fond of the occult. Decisive, but not methodical. Over-confident, transient.

name: Earth Snake
desc: Regarded as wise, but inwardly naive. Prudent, easily scandalized. Possessive.

name: Metal Horse
desc: Sociable, prejudiced, selfish, intolerant. Font of sport and travel.

name: Metal Sheep
desc: Fastidious, conservative, methodical. Dislikes disorder, but does not always have a method.

name: Water Monkey
desc: Audacious, insecure. Hyperactive, manic-depressive. Resents not being taken seriously. Inventive and agile.

name: Water Rooster
desc: Alert, punctual. Frank, abrasive, competitive. Shrewd and precise; extravagant.

name: Wood Dog
desc: Honest, friendly, protective and defensive. Sociable, loyal to friends, reliable.

name: Wood Pig
desc: Content, home and family loving. Practical, acquisitive, industrious.
